{"id":262782,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/11/维权网-无锡拆迁受害人起诉法院不立案，上访遭/","date":"2012-11-13T01:46:15Z","modified":"2012-11-13T01:46:15Z","title":"维权网 | 无锡拆迁受害人起诉法院不立案，上访遭关黑监狱（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员刘娜报道）据无锡拆迁受害人段白梅控诉：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2008</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日</span><span>无锡市锡山区拆迁办，用一张空白的拆迁协议让他们签字被识破后，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">21</span><span>日</span><span>，拆迁办干脆用一张伪造的“拆迁协议”将他们家夷为平地，所有财产被洗劫一空。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">     </span></div>\n<div><span>此后，他们向市、省、国家相关部门反映，但均是出具一份信访转接单，又转回当地解决，可当地就是不解决。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">     </span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月，他们向无锡锡山区法院提起行政诉讼，法院却拒不立案，骗其用民事诉讼，他们改为民事诉讼后，法院还是不立案，致段白梅维权无门。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">      </span></div>\n<div><span>在上访期间</span><span> </span><span>，段白梅夫妻二人经常被关黑监狱：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>人权日那天，他们在北京上访回来后，被关黑监狱</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">39</span><span>天，这样的关押次数数不胜数。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">     </span></div>\n<div><span>段白梅电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13861462388</span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-yp8kSt--pUA/UKEoGHiFFrI/AAAAAAAATU4/lRjVX0EmV5g/s1600/%E9%BB%91%E7%9B%91%E7%8B%B1%E9%97%A8%E5%8F%A3%E6%8A%97%E8%AE%AE.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-yp8kSt--pUA/UKEoGHiFFrI/AAAAAAAATU4/lRjVX0EmV5g/s320/%E9%BB%91%E7%9B%91%E7%8B%B1%E9%97%A8%E5%8F%A3%E6%8A%97%E8%AE%AE.jpg\" width=\"294\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>黑监狱门口抗议</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-2781972584905476157?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}